<p>Ball up the Aluminum Foil then unfold it before putting it in the pan.  Then arrange the Bacon on top of the foil.  It gives the bacon fat places to go instead of having the bacon resting in the grease.  Another idea is to put one layer on the pan then put wire racks in the pan then put more foil over the wire racks. Poke a bunch of holes in the top layer of foil, then arrange your bacon atop the foil covered racks then bake for 15-20 minutes. Perfet Bacon Everytime because the grease drops thru the holes an onto the bottom layer of foil.  Zero Cleanup since the Pan and Rack were protected by foil. </p>
