<p>leave the bacon in longer. 350 degrees in a  circulated oven is more than hot enough, and anywhere from 15-25 minutes. Flip the bacon anywhere after the first 7-10 minutes, depending how fast it is cooking. </p>
<span class="comments-post">Posted by: Dan at November  9, 2010 04:41 PM</span>
